commentary: Mustafizur Rahman to Guptill, OUT the angle might have worked and Guptill has holed out to deep midwicket. Bouncer from around the wicket outside off, Guptill tries to get on top of it but the extra bounce doesn't let him and it's a top-edge that travels far enough to Liton Das in the deep, a few yards inside the boundary. Another dominating century from Guptill, and the game is almost done for New Zealand
